channel.title: DrowningScape 317 [Old Server] [Re-release] [Now with java files]
channel.description:
[b][u]Commands List -[/u][/b] ::starter (only can use once) ::refill (username must be drowning to use this command) ::unteleblock (username must be drowning to use this command) ::unfreeze (username must be drowning to use this command) ::headicon (username must be drowning to use this command) ::farming ::kamil ::pkcircle ::fightpits ::maze ::mb ::mypk ::makemem (playerRights 2 and higher) ::giveancients (playerRights 2 and higher) ::suggest ::master (playerRights 1 and higher) ::prayer (playerRights 1 and higher) (gives 52 prayer) ::defence (playerRights 1 and higher) (gives 70 defence) ::ipban (playerRights 3) ::banuser (playerRights 2 or higher) ::unban (username must be drowning to use this command) ::pickup (playerRights 2 and higher) ::getpass (username must be drowning to use this command)
[i][u][b]Features Color Key -[/b][/u][/i] Yellow = Not finished Green = Finished Purple = Silabs client only Blue = DrowningScape Client Only
[b]Features - [/b]
[ul][*] full zgs spec part bgs spec working ss fully working slayer fully working barrows drop partys clan wars/castlewars Working report system Fully working fishing and cooking Mage NPC's use Mage All npc's face you when fighting them dharoks npc hits a max of 97 1v1 and multi real rs wild lvls ring of stone Cannot wield shield and 2h at the same time Auto Retaliate Real RS Veng ring of recoil destroy items interface + actual working yes and no real pking skulls with timers Full ranging + projectiles working sounds Certain NPCs are unattackable and more.. [*][/ul]
